column5: Another good choice is Golden Fawn Lodge. We've been going there for about 13 years--good facilities, good people, good times...

My party is having some conflicts with the dates we've booked for our trip to Goose Bay. They don't have any other dates that can accomodate our party. Please suggest some other lodges in the Ear Falls area we might try. Thanks.

Just got a call from Evergreen Lodge at Ear Falls, Lac Seul last night. They have openings in June. We had requested a date in June originally and they called me because they had a cancellation. Evergreenlodge.com
Forgot the phone# 807 222 3586 or 888 522 7385 Evergreen Lodge ask for Pat.
Have you been there before? If so, what's it like? BTW, I live in Olathe. Do you fish Lac Seul much?
I live in Olathe too !!! call me Mike 8294887
Here's a neighbor to Evergreen you might try if Evergreen is booked. Golden Eagle Resort: 1-218-262-2732 www.lacseulgoldeneagleresort.com
The correct address for Lac Seul Golden Eagle is;www.lacseulsgoldeneagleresort.com
Winnie, Would love to talk to you call me tonight....Mike ( olathe) 829 4887
We have used Scout Lake resort for years and love it. They are always friendly and helpful. The cabins are very well taken care of and the fishing excellent just off the dock.
